-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
-- Notifications
-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

-- No notifications are defined in this MIB. Placeholder follows.

-- The following two OBJECT IDENTIFIERS are used to define SNMPv2 
-- Notifications that are easily translated into SNMPv1 Traps.

